<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="Aink315">
<l>pāyal koṇṭa paṉimalar neṭuṅkaṭ</l>
<l>pūcal kēḷār cēya reṉpa</l>
<l>viḻainekiḻ cella luṟīik</l>
<l>kaḻaimutir cōlaik kāṭiṟan tōrē</l>
      </lg>
     <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l>They say that he is far away and doesn’t hear the struggles of the long eyes, </l>
<l>resembling flowers, [moisted by] the dew, when they surrender to sleep. </l>
<l>He has traversed the wilderness with groves of ripe bamboos, </l>
<l>causing the distress of slipping jewels. </l>
       </lg>
    </div>
